Don't Go Looking For Monsters | Dark Nature | Free Survival Horror Movie 

While recovering from an abusive relationship, Joy joins her friend's therapy group on an isolated mountainous retreat. Led by a doctor with experimental methods, the group is soon forced to confront a monstrous entity.
2022.  Stars: Madison Walsh, Hannah Emily Anderson, Helen Belay
*Licensed from Epic Pictures. All rights reserved*

*Review* - "Dark Nature" (2022) is a terrifying survival horror movie which serves as a meeting place for psychological terror and creature horror. Initially depicted as a victim of domestic violence, Joy has now taken the first steps to a better life. She then goes on a therapy retreat to the mountains together with other people to meet a doctor whose methods are atypical. However, her way to recover one's identity which initially served as a kind of sacrifice soon turned into a nightmare when the band falls prey to a monstrous entity that lived hidden in the woods. Filled with tension, psychological horror, and primal fear, that full horror movie for free is a must-watch for lovers of survival thrillers, creature features, and terrifying psychological journeys.
